description.en-us: BIGTREETECH Pi 2 uses the higher performance quad-core A55-RK3566 chipset. It consists of rich interface functions, a built-in eMMC5.1, onboard support for 2.4G/5G dual-mode, and WiFi transmission speeds of up to 433.3Mbps.
description.zh-cn: BIGTREETECH Pi 2采用性能更强的四核A55-RK3566芯片组，具备丰富的接口功能，内置eMMC5.1存储器，支持板载2.4G/5G双频模式，WiFi传输速率可达433.3Mbps。
